        .our-story__container
          img.our-story__image(src="images/freedj.avif", alt="Ilias and Josh, founders of GrooveGrid")
          .our-story__text-box
            h1 Our Story
            p
              | GrooveGrid was born out of the passion and vision of Ilias Prevyzis and Josh Fisher, two dedicated individuals who truly understand the challenges faced by emerging talents in the music industry. Both Ilias and Josh have navigated the complexities of pursuing a music career and experienced firsthand the difficulties of breaking into the scene. Their journey inspired them to create a platform that provides real support and valuable opportunities for new artists.
            p
              | They recognized that many talented individuals struggle to get noticed and wanted to build more than just a showcase platform. GrooveGrid is designed to offer artists not only a stage to present their skills but also a comprehensive network database, essential tips and tricks for DJing, and practical advice to help them stand out in a crowded industry. Their goal is to use their combined experience to help guide and support emerging talents.
            p
              | Looking ahead, GrooveGrid aims to expand its offerings to include DJ lessons and more personalized guidance. Ilias and Josh are committed to making the journey easier for new talents and providing the tools and resources needed to succeed. Their mission is to foster a supportive community where artists can thrive and achieve their dreams.

